This paper discusses different forms of server-side blocking, including security concerns and compliance with GDPR regulations. These topics are closely related to computer security (cs.CR), cyber law and policy (cs.CY), and network and communication technologies (cs.SI, cs.DC, cs.SE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
